ap-2 w-full items-center text-center\"><hgroup class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h1 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-4\">393 AC</h1></hgroup></div><div class=\"md-medium md:lg-medium text-neutral-800 flex flex-col w-full items-center text-center\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\"><img alt=\"altered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header\" data-nimg=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"100vw\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F07%2F21170139%2Faltered-news-whispers-from-the-maze-tumult-championships-announcement-header.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"0\"/></p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"timeline\" id=\"widget0_subwidget1\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 px-4 2xl:px-0\"><ul class=\"grid grid-flow-row auto-rows-max grow\"><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">June</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>The exploration forces establish themselves on the surface of the City of Scholars, building a first outpost to recover from the Storhvit trials</li>\n<li>They launch expeditions into the City, which takes the form of a sprawling underground labyrinth stretching across multiple levels and plunging hundreds of meters deep</li>\n<li>Atsadi defeats the Eidolon of Fiore dei Liberi in single combat</li>\n</ul></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">July</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>The new substance found in Caer Nilam seems to have been used in large quantities by the City’s former inhabitants in nearly every aspect of daily life (as an energy source, fertilizer, food, etc.)</li>\n<li>It is named Sap, as it comes from the intensive exploitation of the Nilam. The Asgarthans begin to use it after confirming its harmlessness: the Axioms convert their equipment to counter the Kelon shortage, and Sap is even incorporated into cooking</li>\n<li>Like the Asgarthans, the City’s residents also mastered the use of Aerolith</li>\n<li>Unexpected arrival of the Wayfarer, Lyra Sahanka of Clan Tisdhera.</li>\n</ul></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">August</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>More and more explorers are struck by a strange affliction that steals away their memories</li>\n<li>Some claim to have been targeted by a strange entity, soon called the Hunger. It preys above all on the Sap reserves unearthed by the prospectors</li>\n<li>The writings collected within the City of Scholars suggest that Avalon, far to the northwest, may hold further clues to the location of the Source of the Tumult</li>\n</ul></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\">September</h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\"></h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>The Exalts confront the Hunger and prevail: the entity—revealed to be Sofia, the original incarnation of the City’s soul—is destroyed. It was Sap that had given her life, and when deprived of it, she could only ease her hunger by devouring memories—until madness consumed her</li>\n<li>At her death, she releases a signal in the form of a column of light</li>\n<li>In response, another pillar of light rises on the horizon</li>\n<li>The decision is made to take a detour southwest to investigate the origin of the signal</li>\n</ul></div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "text": "393 AC"
      }
    ]
  },
